âœ… Step 2: File Type Dictionary
File_Types = {
    "Images": [".jpg", ".jpeg", ".png"],
    "Documents": [".pdf", ".docx", ".txt"],
    "Videos": [".mp4", ".mkv"],
    "Music": [".mp3", ".wav"],
    "Archives": [".zip", ".rar"]
}


This dictionary contains:

Folder Name	Extensions
Images	.jpg .jpeg .png
Documents	.pdf .docx .txt
Videos	.mp4 .mkv
Music	.mp3 .wav
Archives	.zip .rar

ðŸ‘‰ Key = Folder name
ðŸ‘‰ Value = List of extensions

