âœ… Step 10: Match Extension With Dictionary
for Folder_Name, extensions in File_Types.items():


This means:

Folder_Name = "Images"
extensions = [".jpg", ".jpeg", ".png"]

âœ… Step 11: Check If Extension Matches
if extension.lower() in extensions:


If:

".jpg" in [".jpg", ".jpeg", ".png"]


Then match found âœ…

âœ… Step 12: Create New Folder Path
